modName: Nord and Elf Male Racemenu Presets
summary: A simple male Preset for Nord and Elf
descriptionHtml:
A simple male Preset for Nord and Elf. This is my first upload so if I did anything wrong, feel free to give me some feeback.

---------------
Installation
---------------
Drag and drop the .nif into skyrim>data>skse>plugins>chargen

and

Drag and drop the .jslot into skyrim>data>skse>plugins>chargen>preset

--------------
uninstall
--------------

Remove the .nif and .jslot from skyrim>data>skse>plugins>chargen and skyrim>data>skse>plugins>chargen>presets
author: MemorieBigTokes
